Package: clawdmeter
Version: 0.7.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.14), libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.5), libayatana-appindicator3-1, libsecret-1-0, libwebkitgtk-6.0-4, libsoup-3.0-0, libvte-2.91-gtk4-0, libcairo2, libpango-1.0-0, bubblewrap, xdg-dbus-proxy
Recommends: gnome-shell-extension-appindicator, tailscale
Suggests: claude (>= 0.3), codex
Maintainer: Darshan Bathija <darshan@defx.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/darshanbathija/Clawdmeter
Description: Live rate-limit gauges and $/token analytics for Claude Code + Codex CLI
 Clawdmeter surfaces live Claude Code and Codex CLI rate-limit gauges in the
 GNOME top bar, plus a dashboard with historical $/token analytics. The
 Sessions chat IDE lets you compose prompts, review plans, accept diffs, and
 merge PRs without leaving the app; iPhone pairing over Tailscale brings the
 same control surface to a phone.
 .
 Targets Ubuntu 24.04+ and ZorinOS 17+. On older LTS releases use the
 AppImage build instead (bundles GTK4 + WebKitGTK 6.0).
